API to Fetch Recent Conversations:


GET /api/chat/recent
API to Fetch Chat History:


GET /api/chat/history/:recipientId?page=1&limit=10
API to Send a Message:


POST /api/chat/send/:recipientId
Body: { "message": "Hello, how are you?" }
API to Get Unread Message Count:


GET /api/chat/unread-count
API to Delete a Conversation:


DELETE /api/chat/delete/:recipientId
API to Search Users by Name or Email:


GET /api/user/search?q=John
API to Mark Chat Messages as Read:


PUT /api/chat/mark-read/:senderId
API to Fetch Chat History for a Specific User:


GET /api/chat/history/:recipientId?page=1&limit=10